These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-1::.
City: boston, london
Job: mechanic, teacher
1. Job:mechanic is in an even position##4
2. Job:teacher == City:london##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |     2      |
| City   | london | boston |
| Job     | teacher    | mechanic   |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-2::.
Nationality: french, american
Sport: sailing, weightlifting
1. Sport:sailing is in an odd position##4
2. Nationality:american is on the left of Nationality:french##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |       2       |
| Nationality   | american | french        |
| Sport      | sailing  | weightlifting |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-3::.
Birthday: october, february
Nationality: canadian, turkish
1. Nationality:canadian is in an odd position##4
2. Birthday:february is on the left of Birthday:october##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |
| Birthday   | february    | october |
| Nationality   | canadian | turkish |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-4::.
